<i>[Anakku] </i>

295
00:31:55,505 --> 00:31:57,705
<i>Nomor yang anda tuju
sedang tidak aktif... </i>

296
00:32:43,408 --> 00:32:44,953
Aku...

297
00:32:49,994 --> 00:32:52,015
