Kongres Noh dengan benar, bukan?

320
00:36:18,798 --> 00:36:20,599
Tentu saja.

321
00:36:22,488 --> 00:36:25,668
Kalau kepala pusat
bakal tahu...

322
00:36:25,668 --> 00:36:27,099
...maka pasti akan rumit.

323
00:36:27,099 --> 00:36:29,499
Ya, aku mengerti.

324
00:36:36,708 --> 00:36:39,708
Ah, Anda pasti dingin.

325
00:36:45,276 --> 00:36:46,575
Terima kasih.

326
00:36:50,458 --> 00:36:53,458
<i>[Berita Terkini - Proses
