330
00:38:14,854 --> 00:38:18,159
Aku tak tahu
harus berbuat apa sekarang.

331
00:38:21,807 --> 00:38:23,208
<i>Ayah akan kembali. </i>

332
00:38:24,309 --> 00:38:26,309
