00:42:16,008 --> 00:42:17,608
Istirahatlah.

354
00:42:37,345 --> 00:42:39,086
Hari ini kerja bagus.

355
00:42:43,958 --> 00:42:46,159
<i>[Ayah] </i>

356
00:42:50,409 --> 00:42:52,961
Halo?/Hei, kau sibuk?

357
00:42:52,961 --> 00:42:54,920
Aku baru mau pulang kerja.
Kenapa?

358
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:57,999
Kemarilah dengan membawa
cairan steril dan perlengkapan obat.

359
00:42:57,999 --> 00:43:01,999
Memangnya ayah di mana?/
Nanti kukirimkan alamatnya.

360
00:43:12,863 --> 00:43:14,463
Augh, beratnya.

361
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:49,420
Hei./Aku di sini.

362
00:43:53,606 --> 00:43:56,905
