biasanya mencari VIP.

416
00:52:01,293 --> 00:52:05,293
Siapa VIP yang Anda bicarakan?

417
00:52:07,693 --> 00:52:10,193
Klien kami...

418
00:52:15,909 --> 00:52:17,517
...dari kejadian Palmunsan.

419
00:52:21,074 --> 00:52:23,807
